headline: DoorDash to Announce First Quarter 2025 Financial Results on May 7, 2025
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, April 01, 2025--DoorDash, Inc. (NASDAQ: DASH) today announced that the company’s first quarter 2025 financial results will be released after the U.S. financial markets close on Wednesday, May 7, 2025. The company’s earnings press release will be made available on the DoorDash Investor Relations website at ir.doordash.com.
